OL,3,CAnti-overdose drug to be made
OL,4,Cavailable without prescription
OL,6,FAn anti-overdose drug is to be made
OL,7,Fmore widely available in England
OL,8,Fwithout a prescription, the government
OL,9,Fhas announced.
OL,11,FThe drug, known as , will be provided
OL,12,Fby professionals, including nurses,
OL,13,Fparamedics, police officers and
OL,14,Fprobation workers, for vulnerable
OL,15,Fpeople to take home.
OL,17,FGovernment plans to update legislation
OL,18,Fwill allow the drug to be given to
OL,19,Ffamily or friends of known opioid
OL,20,Fusers or an outreach worker for
OL,21,Fhomelessness services.
