OL,6,FThe move is part of a 10-year plan
OL,7,Fannounced by the government on Monday
OL,8,Fto "expand and improve the drug and
OL,9,Falcohol treatment and recovery
OL,10,Fworkforce".
OL,12,FMeasures include bringing
OL,13,Fprofessionals into the sector and
OL,14,Fdeveloping better training for
OL,15,Fcurrently unregulated roles.
OL,17,FHealth and Social Care Secretary
OL,18,FVictoria Atkins said: "Opioid
OL,19,Faddiction can ruin lives and is
OL,20,Fresponsible for the largest proportion
OL,21,Fof drug-related deaths across the UK.
